Class ControllerGUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.ControllerGUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Features
    public class ControllerGUI
extends java.lang.Object
implements Features
    A class that represents the controller for the Graphical User Interface. This class implements the Features Interface.
